  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Pension Riedlsperger is a great ski property if you are looking for a relaxing bed and breakfast at an affordable price. This with easy access to the slopes using the local transport, you can be on the mountain in no time.</p>
<h2>Quiet location</h2>
<p>Nestled less than a kilometre from the heart of town, this tranquil spot offers a serene escape from the hustle and bustle, allowing you to unwind amidst peaceful surroundings while still being conveniently close to local attractions and amenities.</p>
<h2>Resort dining</h2>
<p>Guests can savour a delightful breakfast each morning at the Riedlsperger, setting the tone for the day ahead. In the evenings, the town beckons with a diverse array of dining options, perfect for indulging in local delicacies and discovering the region's culinary charm. Whether you're craving traditional flavours or modern cuisine, there's something to satisfy every palate.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Evaldo the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
